MONEY SYMBOLS and all COLLECT FEATURES are active during the feature.

EXTRA CREDIT COLLECT - The value from the EXTRA CREDIT COLLECT symbol is added to all MONEY SYMBOLS currently present on the screen, then all values are added together and paid.

GAME RULES
Pays 1x Total Bet
VOLATILITY
All symbols pay from left to right on selected paylines. All wins are multiplied by bet per line.
MULTIPLIER COLLECT - The value of all MONEY SYMBOLS currently on the screen is multiplied by the value of the MULTIPLIER COLLECT SYMBOL, then all values are added together and paid.
Free spins and bonus wins are added to the payline win.
Free spins total win in the history contains the whole win of the cycle.
Malfunction voids all pays and plays.
Hit 3 BONUS SYMBOLS on reels 2, 3 and 4 to trigger 8 free spins.

EXPANDING COLLECT - All reels that contain at least one MONEY SYMBOL expand to fill the whole reel with MONEY SYMBOLS. The  MONEY SYMBOLS added take a new random value, then all values are added together and paid.
MINIMUM BET:
3x

If one or more MONEY SYMBOLS hit on the screen and any COLLECT SYMBOL hits on reel 5, one of the following features is awarded:
Hit 3 BONUS SYMBOLS on reels 2, 3 and 4 during the FREE SPINS FEATURE to retrigger 8 more free spins. No limits!
When winning on multiple paylines, all wins are added to the total win.
Medium volatility games pay out steadily and the range of pays varies from low to very high

During the feature the value of all MONEY SYMBOLS that hit is added into a bonus pot. After all free spins end the value of the bonus pot is returned to the reels in the form of a giant MONEY SYMBOL on reels 1 - 4, and one final respin is triggered. If COLLECT is hit on reel 5 the value of the bonus pot is paid.
This is the MONEY SYMBOL and it appears on reels 1, 2, 3 and 4.
On each spin the MONEY SYMBOL takes a random value from a predefined set.
There are five types of COLLECT SYMBOLS. They appear only on reel 5.

PAKARTOTINAS SUKIMAS SURENKA - Kai gaunamas PAKARTOTINO SUKIMO SIMBOLIS, visi PINIG SIMBOLIAI esantys ekrane lieka vietoje ir lik stulpeliai pakartotinai sukami, kad parodyt nauj rezultat. Tada vis PINIG SIMBOLI vert rodoma ekrane pakartotino sukimo pabaigoje yra sudedama kartu ir imokta.
SURINKTI - Visos PINIG SIMBOLI verts esanios ekrane yra sudedamos ir imokamos.
TARPO ir ENTER klaviatros mygtukai gali bti naudojami, kad paleist ar stabdyt sukim.
Visi laimjimai ireikti kaip tikri laimjimai monetomis.
PINIG SIMBOLIAI ir visos RINKIMO YPATYBS aktyvios ypatybs metu.
NEMOKAM SUKIM RAUNDO metu naudojamos specialios rits.
EKSTRA KREDIT SURENKAMA - EKSTRA KREDIT SURINKIMO simbolis pridedamas prie vis PINIG SIMBOLI dabar esani ekrane, tada verts sudedamos kartu ir imokamos.
Pasibaigus raundui nemokam sukim laimjimas suteikiamas aidjui.

Visi simboliai imokami i kairs i dein pagal pasirinktinas einamasis linijas.
Visi laimjimai dauginami i statym einamojoje linijoje.
DAUGIKLIO SURINKIMAS  Vis PINIG SIMBOLI verts esanti ekrane dauginama i DAUGIKLIO SURINKIMO SIMBOLIO verts, tada visos vets sudedamos ir imokamos kartu.
Nemokami sukimai ir Bonus laimjimai pridedami prie laimjimo mokjimo eiluts.
Nemokam sukim bendras laimjimas istorijoje laiko viso ciklo laimjim.
Gedimai anuliuoja visus imokjimus ar aidimus.
Surinkite 3 BONUS SIMBOLIUS ant 2, 3 ir 4 rits, nordami aktyvinti 8 nemokamus sukimus.

SURINKIMO IPLTIMAS - Visose ritse yra bent vienas PINIG SIMBOLIS ipleiantis vis  rit su PINIG SIMBOLIAIS. Pridti PINIG SIMBOLIAI gauna nauj atsitiktin vert, tada visos verts sudedamos kartu ir imokamos.
Jei vienas ar daugiau PINIG SIMBOLI gaunamas ekrane ir gaunamas bet kuris SURINKIMO SIMBOLIS ant 5 rits bus gaunama viena i ypatybi:
Surinkite 3 BONUS SIMBOLIUS ant 2, 3 ir 4 rits NEMOKAM SUKIM METU, nordami pakartotinai aktyvinti dar 8 nemokamus sukimus. Be rib!
Jei laimima keliose eilse, visi laimjimai pridedami  bendr laimjim.
Vidutiniko kintamumo aidimai imoka stabiliai ir j mokjimai svyruoja nuo emo iki labai aukto.

Ypatybs metu vis  gaunam PINIG SIMBOLI verts pridedamos  bonus puod.  Po vis nemokam sukim pabaigos bonus puodo verts grainamos  rites miliniko PINIG SIMBOLIO formoje ant rii 1-4 ir aktyvinamas paskutinis pakartotinas sukimas. Jei SURINKIMAS gaunamas ant 5 rits, imokama bonus puodo vert.
Tai yra PINIG SIMBOLIS ant atsiranda ant 1, 2, 3 ir 4 rii.
Kiekvieno sukimo metu PINIG SIMBOLIS paima atsitiktin vert i i anksto nustatyto rinkinio.
Yra penki SURINKIMO SIMBOLI tipai. Jie atsiranda tik ant 5 rits.
